### ============================================================
### MANAGEMENT / INVOICES (confirmed - read-only + status update)
### ============================================================

### List Invoices
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List Invoices (paginated)
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/invoices?page=1&per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Invoice
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/invoices/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update Invoice (status only)
PUT {{base_api_url}}/management/invoices/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "paid"
}

### Download Invoice PDF
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/invoices/1/download
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
